item.content:encoded: The HTTP Archive is a great resource for watching trends on the web in general, and web performance specifically. What you might not know is that data from the HTTP Archive test runs ( twice a month ) are available via Google BigQuery. Ilya Grigorik walks through getting started in HTTP Archive + BigQuery = Web Performance Answers.
